---
title: Smokey Beef & Caramelised Onion Filo Pie with Veggies & Cheddar Cheese
description: This pie must be too good to be true. Get that hit of flavour from caramelised onion tossed through with the beef mince and veggies. It will make your mouth water before it’s even served up. That’s right, this pie is the real deal!

